        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": ["<p><strong>Problem Overview</strong></p>", "<p>This Problem focuses on how unit rate, or constant of proportionality, is helpful to solve problems. Students also look at the role of unit rate in different representations of tables, graphs, and equations.</p>"]
        }
      },
      {"content": {"type": "Text", "format": "html", "text": ["<p>AoL: Synthesis</p>", "<p>CCSSM: 7RP. A.1, 7.RP. A.2, 7.RP.A.2.A, 7.RP.A.2.B,  7.RP.A.2.C, 7.RP.A.2.D, 7.EE.A.2,7.EE.B.3, 7.EE.B.4, 7.EE.B.4.A</p>"]}, "id": "TILEtEauVdS1ctRC"},
      {
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p><strong>Emerging Mathematical Ideas</strong></p>",
            "<p>Introduce the term constant of proportionality and connect it to unit rate.</p>",
            "<p></p>",
            "<p>Use unit rates to solve problems.</p>",
            "<p></p>",
            "<p>Begin to identify and use the constant of proportionality in tables, graphs, and equations and understand how it makes it easy to compare different rates and solve problems.</p>",
            "<p></p>"
          ]
        },
        "id": "TILEL0f12ghPjPfW"
      },
      {
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": ["<p>NWDYK</p>", "<p>Describe how you can determine a unit rate, or constant of proportionality, in a description, rate table, equation, or graph?</p>", "<p>In what ways is a unit rate or the constant of proportionality helpful for solving a problem?</p>"]
